entries.journalEntry: I seem to be ok with what is happening in class. Which makes me happy, buut anxious. Here's to 5 more months.
It was my niece's birthday party. I actually couldn't stop thinking about coding. I keep running over two ideas for my Capstone.
Happy Birthday to me, we haev a Snow Day.
We learned about the GitHub Workflow. I feel in over my head.
After working on this, its hard to say where I feel I am. I feel ok about a lot of my work, and sort of proud I'm trying so hard. I just want to succeed at this.
Second group project.. I hope this isn't terrifying.
I feel like i understand this, but I find it more difficult trying to figure out where to start than anything.
